These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, disco, salsa, country
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, pakistani, canadian, colombian
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, car, motorbike, taxi
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the taxi is between the pakistani and the fan of d&b##2
3. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
5. the japanese is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the canadian is on the right of the fan of disco##1
7. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | salsa      | disco      | country    |
| Nationality   | colombian | japanese | pakistani | canadian |
| Transport     | car    | taxi       | motorbike     | trike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, onion, mango, tomato
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, baking, puzzles, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, drama, horror, family
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
2. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person eating onion##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating onion##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Food          | plum     | tomato     | onion       | mango    |
| Hobby         | baking | puzzles   | rock-climbing | video-games |
| Movie-Genre   | family    | horror | drama    | martial-arts        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, cola, milk
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, indonesian, mexican, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, basketball, parkour, soccer
1. the indonesian is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the mexican##3
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the spanish##3
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite  | cola    | milk |
| Nationality   | mexican   | thai  | spanish  | indonesian    |
| Sport         | basketball    | soccer | water-polo | parkour  |

