.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, pepper, cauliflower, plum
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, spy, crime, comedy
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, snake, chinchilla
1. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person watching spy movies and the person eating corn##2
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the cat is the person eating plum##1
6. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the person eating plum is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | cauliflower   | corn     | pepper | plum |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | comedy | zombie   | spy     |
| Pet           | chinchilla | snake      | hedgehog     | cat       |

