.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, cranberry, zucchini, orange
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, analyst, firefighter, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, mystery, martial-arts, horror
1. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
3. the firefighter is the person watching animation movies##1
4. the chef is between the person eating zucchini and the person eating cranberry##2
5. the firefighter is on the right of the scientist##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person eating orange##1
7. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
8. the person eating zucchini is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
9. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | zucchini      | orange | cranberry      | lemon |
| Job           | analyst | chef | scientist | firefighter   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts    | horror   | mystery     | animation   |

