.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, freelancer, chef, electrician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, classical, d&b, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, swimming, ice-hockey, skiing
1. the person who's sport is swimming is the firefighter##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the fan of disco##1
3. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
5. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
6. the chef is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the freelancer is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
8. the freelancer is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | firefighter    | freelancer   | chef | electrician |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep     | d&b   | disco         | classical        |
| Sport         | swimming | surfing | ice-hockey         | skiing       |

