.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, rock-climbing, woodworking, board-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, project-manager, manager, journalist
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, colombian, malaysian, german
 1. the colombian is on the left or right of the russian##3
 2. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 4. the manager is on the right of the malaysian##1
 5. the malaysian is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the manager is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the malaysian is on the left or right of the journalist##3
 9. the russian is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
10. the project-manager is on the left or right of the manager##3
11. the project-manager is the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | woodworking    | skydiving  | rock-climbing | board-games   |
| Job           | journalist | project-manager   | manager    | software-developer |
| Nationality   | german      | malaysian | colombian | russian  |

