1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | artichoke | cranberry    | onion | nectarine    |
| Hobby         | drawing     | card-games | baking  | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | epic      | family   | comedy         |

