The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, photographer, juicecher, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, satire, comedy, horror
1. the photographer is on the far right##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the chef##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the juicecher is on the right of the scientist##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
7. the scientist is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade    | juice            | 7up     | almond-milk      |
| Job           | chef    | scientist | juicecher     | photographer |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | comedy    | satire | horror    |

