3. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
4. the person eating corn is on the far right##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is the person eating corn##1
6. the american is on the right of the person eating radish##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the argentine##1
8. the person eating banana is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
