3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the librarian is on the right of the designer##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
7. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
8. the person who's sport is basketball is the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
