.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, librarian, security-guard, coach
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, bus, roller, car
1. the coach is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the car is on the right of the librarian##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
6. the person driving the car is between the person driving the bus and the person drinking juice##2
7. the person drinking fanta is the librarian##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage    | fanta   | milk   | juice    | lemonade |
| Job         | librarian | security-guard    | firefighter      | coach |
| Transport   | bus      | car | roller | jet-ski   |

