.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, 7up, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, dancing, gardening
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike, ship, subway
1. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person driving the subway##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
9. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate      | mirinda | tea       | 7up  |
| Hobby       | dancing | camping | gardening    | cooking |
| Transport   | trike     | jet-ski         | ship | subway     |

