4. the owner of the hedgehog is between the police-officer and the thai##2
5. the police-officer is the pakistani##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the lawyer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |      3       |     4      |
