.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, water, milk, fanta
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, fishing, writing, sudoku
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, trike, helicopter, quad-bike
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking water is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the helicopter##2
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
8. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Beverage    | milk   | fanta    | water      | cola |
| Hobby       | collecting  | fishing | sudoku | writing     |
| Transport   | motorbike | trike        | helicopter  | quad-bike        |

