3. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person driving the subway and the person drinking mirinda##2
6. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
