3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the polish is on the far left or far right##3
5. the italian is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
6. the person eating apricot is on the left of the polish##1
7. the person drinking 7up is the egyptian##1
8. the person eating nectarine is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | 7up | water    | milk | soy-milk  |
| Food          | cranberry          | nectarine | apricot       | cauliflower      |
| Nationality   | egyptian     | italian    | german     | polish |

