.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, cherry, watermelon, spinach
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, nurse, mechanic, software-developer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, swimming, cricket, skiing
1. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the doctor##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person eating spinach##1
4. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person eating carrot and the person eating watermelon##2
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
8. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the mechanic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Food    | watermelon | cherry  | carrot  | spinach           |
| Job     | doctor | mechanic | nurse   | software-developer |
| Sport   | skiing   | swimming       | volleyball | cricket  |

 